cs.MM, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG

This paper deals with the analysis of social multimedia content and user behavior modeling, which falls under the scope of several arXiv CS sub-categories. The most likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), as the paper focuses on multimodal content analysis. The second likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), as the paper deals with social media networks. The third likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), as the paper discusses semantic content understanding. The fourth likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), as the paper deals with retrieval tasks. The fifth likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper proposes a novel loss function and embedding model.
